title: Rennes vs PSG | LIGUE 1 HIGHLIGHTS | 10/3/2021 | beIN SPORTS USA
author: beIN SPORTS USA
description:
Gaëtan Laborde and Flavien Tait scored the goals as Rennes ended Ligue 1 leaders Paris Saint-Germain's perfect record, scoring a 2-0 victory at a jubilant Roazhon Park.
